import json
s_result = _input.item.json.output.result
j_result = json.loads(s_result)
item = j_result[0].get("response").get("body").get("items").get("item")
return [{
  "rent_item": item
}]

trades = _input.item.json.trade_item
rents = _input.item.json.rent_item
results = []
for r in rents:
  aptNm = r.get("aptNm")
  ssgCd = r.get("ssgCd")
  deposit = int(r.get("deposit").replace(",", ""))
  for t in trades:
    t_aptNm = t.get("aptNm")
    t_ssgCd = t.get("ssgCd")
    t_dealAmount = int(t.get("dealAmount").replace(",", ""))
    if aptNm == t_aptNm and ssgCd == t_ssgCd:
      addr0 = t.get("estateAgentSggNm")
      addr1 = r.get("umdNm")
      if addr0.count("서울") > 1:
        addr0 = "서울 " + addr0.split("서울")[1].strip()
      full = f"{addr0} {addr1} {r.get('jibun')}"
      full = full.replace(",", "")
      t["full_address"] = full
      
      t["jibun"] = r.get("jibun")
      t["deposit"] = deposit
      t["gap"] = t_dealAmount - deposit
      t["gap_string"] = f'{t["gap"]:,}'
      results.append(t)
      break
return [{
  "result": results
}]

import re
ADDR = _('Set ADDR').item.json
items = _input.all()
level4L = _('Loop Over Items').item.json.response.refined.structure.level4L

def normalize_dong(name: str) -> str:
    # 예외 사전
    exceptions = {
        "종로1·2·3·4가동": "종로동",
        "종로5·6가동": "종로동"
        # 여기에 필요한 예외 더 추가 가능
    }
    if name in exceptions:
        return exceptions[name]

    return re.sub(r"\d+동$", "동", name)

code = ""
normalized_target = normalize_dong(level4L)

for i in items:
  um = i.json.get("읍면동명칭")
  if normalize_dong(um) == normalized_target:
    sido = i.json.get("시도코드")
    gugun = i.json.get("시군구코드")
    dong = i.json.get("읍면동코드")
    code = f"{sido}{gugun}{dong}"
    break

return [{
  "full_address": ADDR.full_address,
  "detail": ADDR.detail,
  "gps_x": ADDR.point.x,
  "gps_y": ADDR.point.y,
  "gps_crs": ADDR.crs,
  "code": code
}]

SGIS = _('SGIS CODE').item.json
result = _input.item.json.result

return {
  "full_address": SGIS.full_address,
  "gps_x": SGIS.gps_x,
  "gps_y": SGIS.gps_y,
  "gps_crs": SGIS.gps_crs,
  "code": SGIS.code,
  "adm_nm": result[0].get("adm_nm"),
  "avg_age": result[0].get("avg_age"),
  "population": result[0].get("population")
}

import re

inputs = _input.all()
# 첫 번째 입력의 result 필드
results = inputs[0].json.get("result", [])
# 두 번째 입력의 datas 필드
datas = inputs[1].json.get("datas", [])

def extract_key(address: str):
    if not address:
        return ""
    # 한글 동/읍/면 + 숫자 지번 추출
    match = re.search(r'([가-힣]+동|읍|면)\s+(\d+)', address)
    if match:
        dong = match.group(1)
        bunji = match.group(2)
        return f"{dong} {bunji}"
    return ""
  
output = []
for r in results:
  rkey = extract_key(r.get("full_address", ""))
  for d in datas:
    dkey = extract_key(d.get("full_address", ""))
    if rkey == dkey:
      print(f"[MATCH] {rkey}")
      # 병합 처리
      r["gps_x"] = d.get("gps_x")
      r["gps_y"] = d.get("gps_y")
      r["avg_age"] = d.get("avg_age")
      r["population"] = d.get("population")
      output.append(r)
      break

return [{
  "results": output
}]
